item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth data type models the billing items created when a CloudLayer storage account generates a bandwidth overage charge. seeAlso SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers.

item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Storage_Hub_Bandwidth data type models the billing items created when a CloudLayer storage account generates a bandwidth overage charge. Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers. Billing items like secondary portable IP addresses fit into this category.
